dmca.title: Trademark Rights of Dr. Ing. h.c. F. Porsche AG
dmca.body:
Dear Sir or Madam:

It has come to our attention that you recently registered PORSCHEV8.COM as a domain name with Register.com, Inc.  We represent Porsche Cars North America, Inc., a wholly owned subsidiary of Dr. Ing. h.c. F. Porsche AG ("Porsche").  Porsche Cars North America, Inc. is the exclusive distributor of PORSCHE
